{"tid":1323915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英女指穆斯林乘客為恐怖份子拒同坐反遭趕落機  有乘客表示大快人心","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T22:02:07.000Z","uid":133680,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a541a0852a1b18db1ee06ce071dae54645f5a94","tid":1323915,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E3%80%91%E9%AC%A7%E5%9B%9E%E6%95%99%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E3%80%8C%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8D%E6%8B%92%E5%90%8C%E6%A9%9F-%E5%85%A9%E6%83%A1%E5%A5%B3%E7%8A%AF%E7%9C%BE%E6%86%8E%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%B6%95%E8%B5%B0%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-180406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25AD%2590%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2583%25A1%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%258A%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%2586%258E%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B6%2595%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-180406&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTed5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=c273b5a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E3%80%91%E9%AC%A7%E5%9B%9E%E6%95%99%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E3%80%8C%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8D%E6%8B%92%E5%90%8C%E6%A9%9F-%E5%85%A9%E6%83%A1%E5%A5%B3%E7%8A%AF%E7%9C%BE%E6%86%8E%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%B6%95%E8%B5%B0%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-180406</a><br />\n<br />\n點到你橫行無忌？兩名英國女子上周四乘搭托馬斯庫克航空(Thomas Cook Airlines)一班從土耳其達拉曼(Dalaman)飛往英國倫敦蓋特威克(Gatwick)機場的客機，登機後，兩人不停謾罵機上3名蓄鬍子的回教男乘客是「恐怖分子」、「是威脅」，又「聲大夾惡」的說不願跟他們同機，要求機組人員將3人趕走。結果機組人員不但沒理會兩人的無理要求，反而召來警員將她們趕下機。<br />\n<br />\n有乘客不值兩名惡女所為，當場拍片記錄其惡行，並在Twitter留言怒斥兩人是「瘋狂的種族主義者(crazy racist)」。片段顯示，其中一名惡女收拾行李，被警員押走，有乘客揶揄，「你這樣(被趕下機)，怎樣返英國呢？」<br />\n<br />\n女乘客克里(Shanea Kerry)事後推文指，兩名惡女見有回教徒同機，初時顯得很懊惱，在機上行來行去，要求空服員將3人趕走但遭拒絕，就稱不想留在機上。克里說，她當時「搭嘴」，反被兩名惡女鬧「肥婊子」，「幾個人說她是種族歧視，她就說我們與這3名男子同機很蠢，我就說，她前往一個伊斯蘭價值觀深種的國家(土耳其)但又歧視穆斯林，就是很愚蠢」。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，該航班延誤1小時20分鐘，航空公司事後亦發聲明表示不接受機上有種族歧視行為，並就事件對乘客造成不便致歉。"},{"pid":"6f8109c6d17675de556a98015e1e3df381e8fc12","tid":1323915,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a38770df0f1eeaa64a7e24e760c0aef072b633","tid":1323915,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40edde0474e5443f06e1b36d07b63de7b5027200","tid":1323915,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3be8374ef109dd05d39b1add0676f3dea209ee","tid":1323915,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1ef532ab9c2547d311e0b66b8c1f105a3dd381","tid":1323915,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T22:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}